<p>After reviewing your exam and other content in the course, we noticed that you were not yet meeting 
  expectations in certain topic areas. Do not worry, these are challenging topics, and it is completely
  fine to not understand them the first time around. However, in order to prepare you for the next exam 
  we wanted to provide you with some resources to improve your understanding of the content area you need 
  to grow in. Please remember, programming is like music; you need to practice to become successful at it.
</p>

<p>
