    sign up for anything, and none of this is required work! It is simply a third party option to present 
    the topic in a different manner. These are intentionally not in a set order. As such, it is alright 
    to find a resource not to your liking and quickly move to the next one. If you find it useful, we 
    encourage you to return to that resource.
</p>

